\n   </ol>\n  ","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"Übersicht","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Das HTML <code>&lt;var&gt;</code> Element repräsentiert eine Variable. Es kann sich dabei um eine mathematischen Ausdruck handeln oder um eine Variable in einem Quellcode.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"dom_interface","title":"DOM Interface","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Dieses Element implementiert das <code><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Element\" title=\"de/DOM/element\">HTMLElement</a></code> Interface.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><strong>Implementationshinweis:</strong> Bis einschließlich Gecko 1.9.2 implementiert Firefox das <a href=\"/de/docs/DOM/span\" title=\"de/DOM/span\"><span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">HTMLSpanElement</span></a> Interface für dieses Element.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"attribute","title":"Attribute","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Keine speziellen vorhanden, nur Universalattribute.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"standardmäßige_style-eigenschaften","title":"Standardmäßige Style-Eigenschaften","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:css notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token selector\">var</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-style</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> italic<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiel","title":"Beispiel","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:xml notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> Eine einfache Gleichung: <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>x<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> = <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>y<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>var</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span> + 2 <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Eine einfache Gleichung: <var>x</var> = <var>y</var> + 2</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html401/struct/text.html#edef-VAR\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 4.01 var</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://dev.w3.org/html5/markup/var.html\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5 var</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"></div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Übersicht","id":"summary"},{"text":"DOM Interface","id":"dom_interface"},{"text":"Attribute","id":"attribute"},{"text":"Beispiel","id":"beispiel"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"}],"summary":"Das HTML <var> Element repräsentiert eine Variable. Es kann sich dabei um eine mathematischen Ausdruck handeln oder um eine Variable in einem Quellcode.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"<var>: The Variable element","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"var","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"<var> : l'élément de variable","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"<var>: 変数要素","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"<var>: 변수 요소","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"<var>","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"<var>","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/html/element/var","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/html/element/var/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML","title":"HTML: HyperText Markup Language"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element","title":"Element"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/var","title":"var"}],"pageTitle":"var - HTML: HyperText Markup Language | MDN","noIndexing":false}}